        <article class='well'>
          <h1>I Love Kippt</h1>
          <p>I've been a Twitter addict for a few years now. The primary reason that I am addicted is that it is my main way of discovering things related to front-end work. Of course, I dig the social part of having tweetversations but the links are my main reason for going.</p>
          
          <p><a href="http://kippt.com">Kippt</a> has provided the best UI and UX that I have seen for link collectors like myself. It is a gorgeous site and has all of the right features for quickly organizing and discovering links. It is a fantastic design and I love it. So, I'm dedicating extra time each day to build up <a href="https://kippt.com/dandenney">my collection</a>. </p>
        </article>
